text: Liliana Scaricabarozzi (born 25 October 1934) is an Italian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
